rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0002
rows.name: Prince Derg, you seem to be enjoying yourself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0004
rows.name:
I won't be able to see Luxaar's face
when he hears my message.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0005
rows.name:
Your Highness, your personality has
certainly taken a turn for the worse.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0007
rows.name: No. I prefer you when you're like this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0008
rows.name: Is that so? Then we're in luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0009
rows.name:
After all, starting today, we have fallen
to being a lawless mercenary band.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs09100100_MSG0010
rows.name: Isn't that right, O fugitive warriors of Lars?![ST:wait ]
